1
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,480
Thousands of years ago,

2
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:37,439
Medicine King Yang chanced upon the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

3
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:41,319
This art uses the body as a furnace to refine the Qi of heaven and earth,

4
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:44,000
with the power to raise the dead.

5
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:49,359
With it, he entered the Dao through medicine and founded the Mystic Medicine Sect.

6
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:54,319
From Medicine Apprentice to Medicine Venerable, the ranks are strict.

7
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:58,879
As ages passed, the sect emerged as the "Mystic Medicine Association."

8
00:01:58,879 --> 00:02:01,799
Yet little did they know, this sect-guarding art

9
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:04,480
had drawn vicious wolves from the shadows.

10
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,239
Hand over the Primordial Violet Qi Art!

11
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,599
Master.

12
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,960
The Mystic Medicine Association

13
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,639
has a traitor within.

14
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,960
I'll make them pay the price.

15
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:29,159
Never let hatred

16
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:30,520
cloud your eyes.

17
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,719
I won't accept it!

18
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,000
Master!

19
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,639
I'll avenge you.

20
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:40,560
Suihua.

21
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,120
What have I done to deserve this?

22
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,400
How did I end up buried alive?

23
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,680
My head is killing me.

24
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:07,960
Where am I?

25
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,000
Who are these people?

26
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,879
And who am I?

27
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,800
The Mystic Medicine Association...

28
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,919
There are traitors among us.

29
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,000
Traitors?

30
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,560
Did these traitors do this to me?

31
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,759
What is this?

32
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:23,840
It's digging into me.

33
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,599
What is this thing?

34
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,240
This emblem looks so familiar.

35
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,840
Maybe this can help me get my memories back.

36
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,199
In the middle of nowhere,

37
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,520
there's a tied-up beauty.

38
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,400
I shouldn't go.

39
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,680
This looks way too much like a trap.

40
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,000
But how could I just stand by and do nothing?

41
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,199
Excuse me.

42
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:40,519
The meridians on her neck radiate outward.

43
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:41,720
Could it be Gu poison flaring up?

44
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,360
My apologies.

45
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,399
Calm outside, chaos within.

46
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,519
Layers of meridians intertwined.

47
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,680
One wrong move decides life or death.

48
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,199
Mother-Child Yin-Yang Gu.

49
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,800
What a vicious scheme.

50
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,800
Violet Qi is favored by the heavens.

51
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,959
Takes physical form, flows through meridians.

52
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:18,439
Purges evil, saves the dying.

53
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:21,680
Only one chosen by fate can wield it.

54
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,079
That amazing?

55
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,759
Where did this handsome guy come from?

56
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,839
What are you looking for?

57
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,000
Don't get me wrong, miss.

58
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,680
I just healed you a moment ago.

59
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,360
Charging a small fee isn't unreasonable, right?

60
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,720
But I don't have any money to pay you.

61
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,959
How about...

62
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:13,240
I offer myself to you?

63
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,120
No need.

64
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,839
That's far too precious.

65
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:19,439
I didn't realize my skills were this good.

66
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,720
A small token will do just fine.

67
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,759
Is this jade pendant yours?

68
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,000
It's quite pretty.

69
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,439
You didn't steal it, did you?

70
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:28,720
When did you take it?

71
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,040
I didn't expect

72
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,519
you to be the one that got away.

73
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,480
Help!

74
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:40,839
Murder!

75
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,240
I can cure the Gu inside you for good.

76
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,600
You don't want to be controlled forever, right?

77
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,839
Why don't we sit down and talk?

78
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,879
You can really cure Gu poison?

79
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,639
Didn't I just treat you a moment ago?

80
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,199
Consider yourself lucky today.

81
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,040
I've got things to do.

82
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,959
I'll let you off for now.

83
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,720
I'll come find you later.

84
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:21,439
I didn't expect you to be the one that got away.

85
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,600
She must know who I really am.

86
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,639
What's this?

87
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:45,240
This emblem looks so familiar.

88
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,639
Mystic Medicine Association.

89
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,639
Who are these people?

90
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,639
The Mystic Medicine Association.

91
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:49,079
And who am I?

92
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:51,199
has a traitor within.

93
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,000
I want to see what monsters and demons

94
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,240
this Mystic Medicine Association is hiding.

95
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,319
Go away.

96
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,120
Lowest-rank Medicine Apprentices are not allowed.

97
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,279
Medicine Apprentice?

98
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,040
What Medicine Apprentice?

99
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,360
No, I'm looking for someone.

100
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:05,199
Get lost.

101
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:07,199
This is the Mystic Medicine Association HQ,

102
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,480
one of the world's top

103
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,560
pharmaceutical organizations.

104
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,480
This is exactly the place!

105
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,160
During the Association's exchange event,

106
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,040
you think you can just waltz in?

107
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,680
Don't be rash.

108
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,120
You stepped on my face!

109
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,160
Who is this guy?

110
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,279
Move aside!

111
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,560
Out of the way!

112
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,600
Step back!

113
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,399
Brother-in-law!

114
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:34,480
Careful!

115
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,399
Watch out!

116
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,080
Medicine Holder Li,

117
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,840
rumor says you've mastered the Four Hall Arts,

118
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,720
both internal and external.

119
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,559
You're said to be the Medicine Venerable's

120
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:48,440
top pick as the next successor.

121
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:48,919
How do you respond to this rumor?

122
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,399
As the youngest Medicine Holder of the Association,

123
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,519
and the rising star of Mystic Medicine,

124
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:52,399
regarding this competition,

125
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,120
will you give it your all?

126
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:55,639
Medicine Holder Li, can you answer our questions?

127
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:59,559
With my abilities, I'm confident

128
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,159
I will secure the prize

129
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:02,960
prepared by the Green Wood Hall,

130
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,720
the "Sea-Calming Tranquility Art,"

131
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,600
for our Crimson Fire Hall.

132
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:09,759
Well said!

133
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,279
Sis! What's wrong, sis?

134
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,759
Sis, are you okay?

135
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:17,799
Sis!

136
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,919
Someone, come here!

137
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,879
Quick, go to my medical vehicle

138
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:22,679
and bring the pain reliever and meridian scanner.

139
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:24,080
Brother-in-law, I'll go!

140
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,279
Hurry!

141
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,279
Medicine Holder Li, what's wrong with your fiancée?

142
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,039
What's going on here?

143
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,639
What kind of illness is this?

144
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,919
Are even you powerless to help?

145
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:32,159
Cold pathogen invasion,

146
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,200
congealing in the uterus.

147
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,759
So I really was an expert before I lost my memory.

148
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,960
Who exactly is he?

149
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,360
Who is this guy?

150
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,120
What are you doing?

151
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:41,759
Who is he?

152
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:42,519
Unauthorized personnel, please leave.

153
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,559
Who told you to touch her?

154
00:09:44,879 --> 00:09:45,840
Saving her comes first!

155
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,679
She has cold congealing in the uterus,

156
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,600
with reversed qi circulation.

157
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,200
One more minute of delay

158
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,399
could cause permanent damage.

159
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,559
I don't need you to tell me that.

160
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,559
A mere Medicine Apprentice like you

161
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:56,759
wants to show off?

162
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,440
Apprentice or not, who cares?

163
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,639
Does rank matter when saving a life?

164
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:03,879
Let him go.

165
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:07,639
Before my equipment arrives,

166
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:09,159
I'll give you a chance.

167
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:12,480
Let's see what tricks you can pull off.

168
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,279
My skills better hold up right now.

169
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,559
Cold congealing in the uterus

170
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:28,000
requires qi as a guide,

171
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,279
flowing through in one breath,

172
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,919
to warm the meridians and dispel the cold,

173
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,919
saving her from the brink of death.

174
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,080
She's awake!

175
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,799
She woke up!

176
00:10:40,799 --> 00:10:41,519
A miracle doctor!

177
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,120
Move aside!

178
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:44,600
Scram!

179
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,080
Stop filming!

180
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,919
Miracle doctor!

181
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:04,639
Don't go!

182
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,679
Miracle doctor, don't go!

183
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,279
Did he save me?

184
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:10,360
He actually cured what Xiangyang couldn't.

185
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,720
Stop following me.

186
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,320
He's pretty handsome.

187
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:27,120
This little Medicine Apprentice is interesting.

188
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:30,120
Xiaoqiu, keep a close eye on him.

189
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:32,240
I want him.

190
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:33,440
Understood.

191
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,480
Do you know what just happened outside?

192
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,720
Confirm if all the contestants are here.

193
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:41,480
Send someone to deliver the contestants' files.

194
00:11:57,879 --> 00:11:59,679
"Sea-Calming Tranquility Art."

195
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:01,679
The same emblem.

196
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:03,440
It must be tied to my identity.

197
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,200
I have to get my hands on it.

198
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,600
Hey, buddy.

199
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,600
What is this thing?

200
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,039
You must be new here.

201
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,240
You don't even recognize this?

202
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:17,759
This is the Yang family's sect-guarding art,

203
00:12:17,759 --> 00:12:19,080
"Sea-Calming Tranquility Art."

204
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,440
It's not something you can just touch.

205
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:29,080
Then this whatever-it's-called Art,

206
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,519
how can I take it?

207
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,399
Take it?

208
00:12:34,399 --> 00:12:35,840
You really know how to crack a joke.

209
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:38,720
It's the grand prize of the Mystic Medicine tournament.

210
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:42,200
It's just on display for everyone to admire.

211
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,679
Win the contest, and you can take it.

212
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:46,960
Then how do I enter?

213
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,679
Where do I sign up?

214
00:12:48,519 --> 00:12:50,840
You think just anyone can compete?

215
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,759
Look at that Medicine Apprentice uniform you're wearing.

216
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:57,320
You're not even qualified to watch.

217
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,720
And you want to win first place?

218
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:01,879
Pack up and get back to your chores.

219
00:13:04,519 --> 00:13:05,559
Finally found you!

220
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,960
Miss Lu.

221
00:13:23,559 --> 00:13:24,879
If he's your guest,

222
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,799
I was blind not to see it.

223
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:28,960
Please forgive me.

224
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,840
I didn't get a chance to thank you earlier.

225
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:39,120
Are you here to watch the competition?

226
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:41,840
Sort of.

227
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:44,840
Actually, I'd rather compete.

228
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:48,120
Competing might be difficult,

229
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,360
because every contestant

230
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,720
is recommended by a Medicine Master of their hall.

231
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,480
But take this for now.

232
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,600
You should be able to watch the matches with it.

233
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:59,120
Consider it a small token of thanks.

234
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,960
Then I won't refuse.

235
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,440
By the way,

236
00:14:03,799 --> 00:14:05,080
did you happen to see

237
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:05,799
an exceptionally beautiful

238
00:14:05,799 --> 00:14:06,919
woman in red walk in?

239
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:17,200
Your girlfriend?

240
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,600
Don't talk nonsense.

241
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,639
I don't have a girlfriend.

242
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,279
I have real business with her.

243
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,559
This woman

244
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,919
still owes me my consultation fee.

245
00:14:28,919 --> 00:14:30,120
You're quite an interesting one.

246
00:14:31,639 --> 00:14:32,240
Miss Lu,

247
00:14:33,159 --> 00:14:33,879
Someone's looking for you.

248
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:34,759
Okay.

249
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:37,360
Try to watch more and speak less.

250
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:40,120
Today's competition is no ordinary match.

251
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:43,279
It's a showdown between our Association's Traditional and Tech factions.

252
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,799
Miss Lu!

253
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,840
Coming.

254
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,159
You should go.

255
00:14:48,879 --> 00:14:50,799
Just make sure you don't get into trouble.

256
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:51,440
Don't worry.

257
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,759
Xiangyang's condition can barely be contained.

258
00:15:00,759 --> 00:15:03,440
This time we must get it from that old fossil Ye Zhentian:

259
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,519
the "Sea-Calming Tranquility Art."

260
00:15:04,519 --> 00:15:06,639
Relax, leave Number Zero to me.

261
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:15,440
I didn't expect you to be the one that got away.

262
00:15:16,159 --> 00:15:17,600
She must know my identity.

263
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,720
Where did he run off to now?

264
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,879
You, Medicine Apprentice!

265
00:15:32,879 --> 00:15:33,840
How dare you slack off?

266
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:35,519
I'm...

267
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:36,480
Don't "I'm" me!

268
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,559
Come with me to deliver supplies to the contestants' lounge.

269
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:39,440
Did you hear me?

270
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,200
The competition starts soon.

271
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:41,559
Take it, hurry!

272
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:45,720
The contestants' lounge?

273
00:15:47,519 --> 00:15:48,200
Perfect.

274
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:51,120
My chance has just arrived.
